comment: Pachulia (MIL) sets the screen on Pondexter (NOP) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Pondexter (NOP) contests the jump shot and gives Middleton (MIL) the opportunity to land.
Asik (NOP) shuffles his feet after coming to a jump stop.
Gordon (NOP) does not maintain legal guarding position as his forearm and body contact affect Bayless's (MIL) RSBQ.
Pachulia (MIL) never stops moving while setting the screen on Gordon (NOP) and preventing him from contesting the jumpshot.
RHH, LATR and L-Slash show Middleton (MIL) hit Evans's (NOP) arm on the play to the basket, causing him to lose control of the ball.
Davis (NOP) makes body to body contact with the airborne Bayless (MIL) and the contact affects his movement to the basket.
Bayless (MIL) makes contact on the perimeter that does not affect Gordon's (NOP) RSBQ.
After Bayless (MIL) picks up his dribble, Middleton (MIL) requests a timeout. However, the timeout is not granted until after Bayless loses possession of the ball trying
Pachulia (MIL) sets the screen on Davis (NOP) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
